        <abstract> 
<p>Dimorphism in <hi rend="italic">Linum</hi>.</p> 
            <p>Situation in some of the lower Algae is analogous to that in phaenogams. In some, conjugation occurs between separate filaments, in others between cells of same filament.</p> 
<p>Forwards a letter from S. O. Glenie enclosing specimens of <hi rend="italic">Cassia fistula</hi> which show the two forms of the anthers.</p> 
        </abstract>
